---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Astro Content Lab">
  <div class="about">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>About Astro Content Lab</h1>
      <p>A demo project built live, documented step by step.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <h2>What is this?</h2>
      <p>Astro Content Lab is the demo project for the series <strong>"Learn Astro from Scratch — Build a Real Content Site"</strong>. Every page, every component, every bug and fix was built in real time and documented in the series articles.</p>

      <h2>Who built this?</h2>
      <p>Steven Doan — a freelance web developer from Vietnam who spent 10+ years building WordPress sites before learning Astro. This project documents that transition honestly, including every mistake along the way.</p>

      <h2>What does this site have?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Blog posts written in Markdown and MDX</li>
        <li>Review pages with rating, pros, cons and verdict</li>
        <li>Comparison pages with winner and verdict</li>
        <li>Guide pages with difficulty level and estimated time</li>
        <li>Content Collections with schema validation</li>
        <li>Plain CSS styling — no framework</li>
        <li>Deployed on Vercel via GitHub</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Source code</h2>
      <p>The full source code is public on GitHub. Each commit maps to a specific article in the series.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/doancongtuan/astro-content-lab" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">View on GitHub →</a>

      <h2>Read the series</h2>
      <p>The full series is published on doancongtuan.com — a practical guide for WordPress users who want to understand how modern static sites work.</p>
      <a href="https://doancongtuan.com" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">doancongtuan.com →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .page-header h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .page-header p { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; }

  .about-body {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.375rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>